title: Stop Crypt CMD Paramaters
id: 29c87ffe-bb8b-49cc-9409-582d112c84d0
status: experimental    
description: Detects suspicious commandline parameters (–-Admin IsNotAutoStart IsNotTask) for created processes.  These parameters are utilized in Stop Crypt Ransomware execution.
references:
    - https://blog.sonicwall.com/en-us/2024/03/new-multi-stage-stopcrypt-ransomware/
author: Tyler Casey @1qazCasey, @scythe_io
date: 2024/04/04
tags:
    - attack.execution
    - attack.t1059
logsource:
    product: windows
    category: proc_creation
detection:
    selection:
        CommandLine|endswith:
            - '--Admin IsNotAutoStart IsNotTask'
    condition: selection
falsepositives:
    - Legitimate paramaters for an executable.
level: 
    - high
